# ============================================================
# ITEM CORE RUNTIME
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: runtime
domain: item
scope: item.core
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

## purpose
Defines core runtime handling for item.

## runtime_scope
Runtime covers item visibility,
possession-aware display,
placement-aware display,
usage/transfer state,
historical item reference,
and safe failure rendering.

## validation_rules
- item identity must resolve
- possession basis must resolve
- placement/use/transfer scope must resolve
- disclosure scope must be valid

## failure_modes
- invalid item identity
- invalid possession basis
- invalid use/transfer scope
- safe runtime fallback

## observability
Runtime must emit enough signals
to distinguish item state,
possession state,
placement/use state,
historical reference,
and failure surface.

## review_checklist
- item runtime scope is explicit
- possession-aware rendering is explicit
- failure handling is explicit
